post_text: Cedar Tree Academy will continue to follow DCPS system and remain closed through April 24, 2020, with classes resuming on Monday, April 27, 2020. Cedar Tree Academy will continue our distance learning program while the school is closed.
text: Cedar Tree Academy will continue to follow DCPS system and remain closed through April 24, 2020, with classes resuming on Monday, April 27, 2020. Cedar Tree Academy will continue our distance learning program while the school is closed.

post_text: Cedar Tree Academy will be closed for students from March 16th to March 31st. From March 24th to March 31st, students will participate in distance learning and home-bound assignments. Meals will be available for students every weekday at sites across the district.

post_text:
Ebony Harris is new to Cedar Tree Academy this year, and she brings a wealth of passion and knowledge. Mrs. Harris teaches and motivates young scholars about different systems of the body, keeping their bodies healthy and strong, and staying active. She also has fostered varies community organizations' relationships on behalf of the school. Ms. Harris states “The most important thing to me is to try and inspire my scholars; so, they can be great at whatever they want to be.”

#LTLT #CharterSuccess #RootedInEducation #DcCharterProud
